HEADWORD: Ineradicable
<hw>In`e*rad"i*ca*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Incapable of
being eradicated or rooted out.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The bad seed thus sown was <qex>ineradicable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Ld. Lytton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ineradicably</ent>⟦br⟧
